Architecture:
        - Handler (HansVisual)
        - Layer
        - Graphics engine (plotter)
        - Shaders
	- Controls
	- Camera
	- GUI
	- Window
You save vertex in a certain format in a layer (handler > layer).
Data from layer is sent to graphics engine (layer > handler > graphics engine).
Controls are managed (controls > handler)

